title: TextMage 2.3.2 Final Incl. Crack-LAXiTY [ATOM]

Description:
TextMage is a handy and reliable text editor that was especially designed to help you handle text files and multiple files at once.

The powerful functions of TextMage include search and replace, regex support, line filtering and many more. Also, the application supports batch processing, so you can load several files and they can be edited simultaneously.
